code: @Override public boolean filter(T value, Context<T> ctx) throws Exception {     return getLeft().filter(value, ctx) && getRight().filter(value, ctx). }

comment: /**  * @return One of the {@link IterativeCondition conditions} combined in this condition.  */
code: /**  * @return One of the {@link IterativeCondition conditions} combined in this condition.  */ public IterativeCondition<T> getLeft() {     return getNestedConditions()[0]. }

comment: /**  * @return One of the {@link IterativeCondition conditions} combined in this condition.  */
code: /**  * @return One of the {@link IterativeCondition conditions} combined in this condition.  */ public IterativeCondition<T> getRight() {     return getNestedConditions()[1]. }
